title: Tornado threat cancels Trump's Iowa rally as Ron DeSantis campaigns in the state
description: A tornado watch forced Donald Trump to abruptly cancel an outdoor rally in Iowa Saturday, the same day Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis was campaigning in the state.

title: How a rural Arkansas prosecutor advocated for her pedophile uncle
description: One of Barry Walker’s victims, now 22, blamed those close to Walker for not stopping him before he sexually abused more than 30 girls. “They failed us,” she told NBC News.

title: Pop — and politics — will be on display as Britain hosts a Ukrainian-hued Eurovision song contest
description: As it hosst the Eurovision Song Contest, the U.K. city of Liverpool is ablaze with the blue and yellow of the Ukraine flag, over a year after Putin's invasion.

title: China unlikely to play peacemaker role in Ukraine war, Western officials and experts say
description: The Biden administration and U.S. allies doubt China can play a decisive role in bringing an end to the Ukraine war, Western diplomats and ex-U.S. officials say.

title: Social Security advocates brace for U.S. debt default: Seniors should 'be prepared'
description: With the odds of a U.S. debt default increasing, Social Security advocates warn beneficiaries they should be prepared in case their payments are interrupted.

title: Ron DeSantis is a hot ticket at GOP events
description: Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis has been selling out venues, breaking local fundraising records and forcing organizers to move into larger spaces.
